c: 7
v: 143
t: "When Moses ven our appointed temp his Lord parol kun him li dir My Lord let me jen vid Vi, Li dir Vi ne seg Me Jen je ke mont se gxi rest its ej tiam vi seg Me Tiam his Lord manifested mont this kauxz gxi cxif! Moses fal unconscious When li ven li dir Vi glor. Mi pent Vi mi plej konvink believer"